          <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.6">Users claim milestones by submitting structured evidence — not self-declaration. Each badge has specific evidence prompts. A founder claiming "First Revenue" describes their revenue model and timeline. An investor claiming "First Check" names the company and round. This evidence creates the richest participant dataset in AgTech.</div>
