          <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.6">Four-tier progression: Explorer (0+ badges), Builder (3+), Operator (6+), Leader (9+). Tiers reflect verified engagement, not vanity metrics. A Leader-tier investor has proven portfolio activity — they can set preferences to only connect with Operator+ founders. Quality controls quality.</div>
