          <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.6">Users are prompted monthly to confirm their profile is current and claim new milestones. Color-coded urgency (green → yellow → red) keeps the ecosystem fresh. New accounts use their creation date as baseline. Stale profiles lose visibility. "Nothing changed" fast-path respects busy users while still recording engagement.</div>
